<item>
            <title>[SOLR-6752] Buffer Cache allocate/lost metrics should be exposed</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-6752</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, &lt;tt&gt;o.a.s.store.blockcache.Metrics&lt;/tt&gt; has fields for tracking buffer allocations and losses, but they are never updated nor exposed to a receiving metrics system. We should do both. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
